陸媒也報導，目前業界除了順豐之外，所有的快遞員都沒有底薪，因此刪減送貨費釀成了快遞員罷工，<span class=\"red\">而這也突顯出快遞業削價競爭的發展困境</span>。（編輯：沈朋達）1091018<br />\n<br />\n令我諗起中國人做生意個張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T16:53:51.000Z","msg":"1件先0.5，咁辛苦，係網到做5毛打下字仲好啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T02:20:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa03f938fa7fa801dee24fb74154b52d62c07ad5","tid":2248581,"uid":2360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T02:24:25.000Z","msg":"假新聞喇 中國人成世食草都沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nGDP繼續go go go<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L4Aoaa6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL4Aoaa6.png&h=dada6491&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"157d019be857e577de4ee9ee2857744f7b4c7100","tid":2248581,"uid":190789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T02:28:26.000Z","msg":"相信黨，唔驚"},{"pid":"8a56720d6aba0ec5df0dc3f94214e703df2f5030","tid":2248581,"uid":364850,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b751ce3e884fe16959a74f55fd1f5f230c1ba1fd","tid":2248581,"uid":126283,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5eb3c05c94de1b4b7f783882ea41558bbe76a7c2","tid":2248581,"uid":12628,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"quote":{"pid":"301c005b225ead63e43fc2004f756e0195e36e0e","tid":2248581,"uid":253608,"like":121,"dislike":0,"score":121,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T16:52:54.000Z","msg":"陸媒都市時報報導，由於物流成本上漲，有快遞公司選擇刪減快遞員的送貨費，來節省開支，送貨費從原先的<span class=\"red\">每件人民幣1.2元（約新台幣5.12元），被大砍到0.5元</span>，因而釀成罷工。<br />\n<br />\n據香港01統計，這次罷工的快遞員來自中通、韻達、百世和圓通等公司，而受影響的包括湖南長沙、福建三明、河北、江蘇蘇州和吉林長春等地。<br />\n<br />\n中國的電商經濟，帶動了快遞業發展。微信公眾號紫財經指出，<span class=\"red\">包括順豐、韻達、百世、申通、圓通和中通等企業都已